rows.label: qst500102_msg0003
rows.name:
Monono get on ship to go back to
home at Avaritia Trade Guild...

rows.label: qst500102_msg0004
rows.name: But ship take long time to set sail.

rows.label: qst500102_msg0005
rows.name:
Monono overhear things about
Superbia too. Did Monono get
on wrong ship?!

rows.label: qst500102_msg0007

Was not expecting that!

rows.label: qst500102_msg0009
rows.name:
Monono must hurry back to Avaritia
and deliver tasty Mint Fish to others!

rows.label: qst500102_msg0010

If friends stop by Avaritia, be sure
to visit Twelve Brothersisterpon!
